      };
    }

Note that we&#39;ve changed the `key` to something that uniquely identifies the _element_ we&#39;re building a `&lt;p&gt;` for: never use array index as key, because array position does not identify any specific _element_, it only identifies a _position_ in a list.

Also note that there&#39;s no reason to pass more than just the room number in your click handler if the handler itself only cares about the room number.

