You can&#39;t access a variable directly in another class. You need a reference to the class to access the variable. So the code should be:

    app.mainp.add(red);

Now in your MainFrame class you need to use:

    public JPanel mainp = new JPanel();

to give other classes permission to access the variable directly.

Note, this is NOT a good design. You should generally NOT make &quot;public&quot; variables.

Instead you should create a method in the `MainFrame` class:

    public JPanel getMainPanel()
